  <?dbhtml dir="listComponent"?>
  <title>Concrete toolkit list component</title>
  <para>
  	A <emphasis>list</emphasis> is a component which displays a number of values. Lists allow single or multiple
  	values to be selected. 	
  </para>
  <para>
  	Because the comma (,) is a special symbol for lists, if you want to use a comma as part of your parameter value,
  	you have to mask it.
  </para>
